constituent: frame, tree, wood, ninety, nine, baseball, ten, needle
heisigStory: You might think of the frame this character refers to as the sort of frame we have created by drawing a dark line around this kanji and its explanation. Then think of that line as made of very thin wood; and finally note how each time the line bends it forms a 90° angle, thus giving us the nine and the ten.
koohiiStory2: Nine out of ten picture frames are made out of wood. The rest are made of metal or plastic.
myStory: khung. gỗ chặt 9 10 khúc làm khung
